+ * @SI5351_VARIANT_A3: Si5351A MSOP10 (3 output clocks, XTAL input)
+ * @SI5351_VARIANT_B: Si5351B (8 output clocks, XTAL/VXCO input)
+ * @SI5351_VARIANT_C: Si5351C (8 output clocks, XTAL/CLKIN input)
