+ * @SI5351_MULTISYNTH_SRC_DEFAULT: default, do not change eeprom config
+ * @SI5351_MULTISYNTH_SRC_VCO0: multisynth source clock is VCO0
+ * @SI5351_MULTISYNTH_SRC_VCO1: multisynth source clock is VCO1/VXCO
